        <item>
            <title>1.8.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 15:00:32 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>62</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 1.8.1</h2>
<p><strong>Added</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Added TelemetryDeck funnel tracking for the first rename flow</li>
<li>Added country to new install Telegram notifications</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Improved</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kept the AI Rename prompt visible until valid files are actually added</li>
<li>Added explicit consent and unsupported-file feedback in AI Rename</li>
<li>Recovered dropped files through onboarding and consent setup automatically</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Fixed</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed duplicate new install notifications from concurrent status checks</li>
<li>Reduced duplicate status refreshes during app launch</li>
<li>Added better Sentry capture for analysis and rename failures</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
